# textdomain: mcl_clock
Clocks are tools which shows the current time of day in the Overworld.=时钟显示世界上当前时间的工具。
The clock contains a rotating disc with a sun symbol (yellow disc) and moon symbol and a little “pointer” which shows the current time of day by estimating the real position of the sun and the moon in the sky. Noon is represented by the sun symbol and midnight is represented by the moon symbol.=时钟包含一个带有太阳符号（黄色圆盘）和月亮符号的旋转圆盘，以及一个小「指针」，通过估计太阳和月亮在天空中的实际位置来显示当前的时间。正午由太阳符号表示，午夜由月亮符号表示。
Clock=时钟
Displays the time of day in the Overworld=显示世界上当前的时间
